fr.ign.cogit.cartagen.spatialanalysis.network.railways

Class ParallelRailsGroup

  • Object
    • ParallelRailsGroup

  • public class ParallelRailsGroup
extends Object
    A model to group parallel tracks of railways, in order to collapse them properly. The model is described in (Savino & Touya 2015).
    Author:
    GTouya
